TITLE: Sahasrara Kriya | Water Fire Tandavam | Noorism Project 888
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lWEq367W8vc
DATE: 11 January 2026 (Sunday, 2:00 PM — explicitly stated in the video)
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Recorded on January 11, 2026 (a Sunday at 2:00 PM), Maa delivers an urgent prophetic message from her bed, explaining that she has been unable to make videos due to an intense ongoing kriya. The primary revelation is that Kalki's Sahasrara (Crown Chakra) Activation Process is now actively underway, and the next phase involves the activation of Agni (fire). She warns that fire will spontaneously ignite in impossible places — walls will catch fire, floors will catch fire, water will catch fire, ice will catch fire — without any human cause. No one will be able to understand how or why these fires started. These are not accidental fires but manifestations of Kalki's Sahasrara Kriya operating through cosmic energy.

Maa explains that Kalki has now moved beyond the physical body — operating from outside the body — and all activity is now happening from that transcendent state. She references her previous video where she explained that Kalki's next process involves the head region, connecting it to Khatu Shyam Ji, Ganesh Ji, Rahu, Kirti Mukh, Panchmukhi Hanuman Ji (five-faced Hanuman), and Panchmukhi Shiva — indicating that Kalki has assumed or aligned with this Panchmukhi (five-faced) divine form for the Sahasrara activation.

She issues a direct warning: take care of small children — keep them close 24 hours a day, never let them out of sight. Take care of your homes — even if the house is locked and empty, fire can spontaneously ignite inside. The coming times will be very difficult for everyone. She emphasizes that humans can do nothing now; everything is in Paramatma's (God's) hands. The only instruction is to connect with Paramatma and hold on to the divine hand.

Maa also shares that these kriyas cause her physical body immense suffering — they are not symbolic or in name only. She must physically travel wherever she is directed to complete each process, and only upon completion does she receive the next set of messages and divine instructions. She requests support (bhiksha/donations) from followers since Paramatma has ordered that all her journeys must be undertaken through bhiksha, and in Kaliyuga nothing is possible without money.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Kalki's Sahasrara (Crown Chakra) Activation Process is now actively underway as of January 2026
- The next phase is the activation of Agni (divine fire) — fire will spontaneously and inexplicably ignite everywhere: in walls, floors, water, ice, closed houses, any surface
- No human agency will be behind these fires — they are direct manifestations of cosmic energy through Kalki's kriya
- Kalki has moved beyond the physical body — now operating from outside the body; all activity is from a transcendent state
- The Sahasrara kriya involves the head region, connecting to: Khatu Shyam Ji, Ganesh Ji, Rahu, Kirti Mukh (Face of Glory), Panchmukhi Hanuman Ji, and Panchmukhi Shiva
- Kalki has assumed the Panchmukhi (five-faced) Shiva form for this process
- Direct warning: keep small children close at all times; never leave them unattended
- Direct warning: watch over your homes — spontaneous fires can occur even in locked, empty houses
- The coming times will be extremely difficult for everyone
- Humans have no power in this phase — everything is in Paramatma's hands
- Maa's physical body suffers immensely during each kriya — these are not symbolic processes
- Paramatma has ordered that all of Maa's journeys must be undertaken through bhiksha (alms/donations)
- Maa cannot proceed to the next kriya until the current one is completed through physical travel to designated locations
- Maa explicitly tells Kalki's team they were chosen for a reason and should make effort to understand the messages themselves

TIMELINE EVENTS:
- 11 January 2026: This message recorded; Sahasrara Activation Process confirmed as actively underway
- 11 January 2026: Prophetic warning about spontaneous divine fire (Agni activation) issued
- Previous video (before Jan 11, 2026): Maa revealed that Kalki's next process involves the head/Sahasrara region
- Ongoing as of Jan 2026: Kalki operating from beyond the physical body
- Ongoing: Maa unable to make videos due to intensity of the kriya affecting her body
- Future (imminent): Spontaneous unexplainable fires to begin manifesting worldwide
- Future: Coming times declared to be very difficult for everyone

ORIGINAL HINDI KEY QUOTES:
- "11 जनवरी 2026 आज संडे है" = "January 11, 2026, today is Sunday"
- "कल्कि की जो क्रिया है वह सहरसरा एक्टिवेशन प्रोसेस चल रहा है" = "Kalki's kriya — the Sahasrara Activation Process — is underway"
- "जो आग है वह एक्टिव हो गई है। अग्नि।" = "The fire has been activated. Agni."
- "पानी में आग पकड़ लेगी। बर्फ में आग पकड़ लेगी। दीवारों में आग।" = "Water will catch fire. Ice will catch fire. Walls will catch fire."
- "आप समझ ही नहीं पाओगे कि यह आग कैसे लगी। किसने लगाई और कैसे लगी।" = "You will not be able to understand how this fire started. Who started it and how it started."
- "अब जो कल्कि है जो वो अपने इस शरीर से बाहर हैं। उनका कहना है कि वो उस शरीर से बाहर है। अब सारी एक्टिविटी जो उस शरीर से बाहर है।" = "Now Kalki is outside this body. They say they are outside that body. Now all activity is from outside that body."
- "पंच मुखी शिवा अपने इस उस रूप में आ गए हैं" = "Panchmukhi Shiva has assumed that form"
- "छोटे बच्चों को बिल्कुल भी अपने से दूर मत रखिए। 24 घंटे उन पर निगाह रखिए।" = "Do not keep small children away from you at all. Keep your eyes on them 24 hours."
- "इंसान का अब कुछ नहीं है" = "Humans have nothing [no power/control] now"
- "अपने आप को परमात्मा के साथ जोड़िए। और उनका हाथ पकड़ लीजिए।" = "Connect yourself with Paramatma. And hold on to Their hand."
- "मेरा शरीर झेलता है इन क्रियाओं को। कष्ट है इन क्रियाओं में।" = "My body endures these kriyas. There is suffering in these kriyas."
- "मुझे जो भी यात्राएं करनी है वो भिक्षा लेकर ही करनी है" = "Whatever journeys I have to make, I must make them only through bhiksha (alms)"

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: This video marks a critical escalation point in the Yug Parivartan process. The Sahasrara (Crown Chakra) Activation of Kalki represents the highest energy center being activated — the crown is the gateway to cosmic consciousness and divine authority. The activation of Agni (fire) as a spontaneous, uncontrollable force of nature signals the transition from subtle spiritual processes to overt physical manifestations that the entire world will witness. The "Water Fire Tandavam" in the title refers to the paradoxical divine dance where even water and ice catch fire — the fundamental laws of nature being overridden by divine will. This is Shiva's Tandavam manifesting through elemental forces. Kalki moving beyond the physical body signifies transcendence into a purely cosmic operational mode. The Panchmukhi (five-faced) form — connecting Khatu Shyam, Ganesh, Rahu, Kirti Mukh, and Panchmukhi Hanuman/Shiva — represents the complete assembly of divine aspects needed for the Sahasrara activation. Noorism Project 888 is the overarching spiritual project framework within which these kriyas operate. The direct warnings about protecting children and homes indicate that the Yug Parivartan is entering a phase of tangible, physical-world impact that will affect all of humanity.


